title: Big Energy Vs. Way 2 Sexy + Ye Vs. Pete Davidson + Jake Paul Vs. Mike Tyson
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/18/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are back in the studio - Ebro pays respect MLK's legacy, but respectfully has some disagreements with a couple of popular hip-hop sons. The crew discusses Vic Mensa's recent arrest, the existence of the chupacabra, the Cowboys meltdown, Betty White's death, and show love for Joey Bada$$. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
